- Lampu, siap?

469
00:35:03,810 --> 00:35:06,437
- Hei, lampu.
- Sebentar.

470
00:35:06,521 --> 00:35:08,106
Semuanya siap.

471
00:35:08,189 --> 00:35:10,399
Bedebah ini tampak sangat manis hari ini.

472
00:35:10,483 --> 00:35:13,444
- Berhenti.
- Diamlah sebentar, Jun-ho.

473
00:35:14,028 --> 00:35:15,655
