554
00:41:31,447 --> 00:41:33,365
<i>Halo, Bu Pengacara.</i>

555
00:41:33,949 --> 00:41:36,994
Pengacara para korban
baru saja meneleponku.

556
00:41:37,077 --> 00:41:40,331
Aku disuruh datang ke kantor Taebaek
pada pukul 18.00 untuk berdamai.

557
00:41:40,998 --> 00:41:43,292
Taebaek juga meneleponmu?

558
00:41:43,375 --> 00:41:44,543
Ya.

559
00:41:44,627 --> 00:41:46,462
<i>Aku mengerti siasat mereka.</i>

560
00:41:47,004 --> 00:41:49,590
<i>Mereka meminta uang damai</i>
<i>sebesar 150 juta won.</i>

561
00:41:49,673 --> 00:41:54,261
Mereka pasti menduga Pengacara Shin
tak akan menyetujui nilai sebesar itu,

562
00:41:54,345 --> 00:41:55,971
